{
  "info": {
    "name": "Court Record Check (CRC) \u2014 Idfy Webhook Receive Path",
    "description": "Exercises the CRC receive path end-to-end against the running driver-app: an Idfy 'ind_court_record' webhook is delivered, parsed, routed to the CRC branch (driverId via group_id, row-less), and stored as JSON on driver_identity_info.court_record.\n\nSELF-CONTAINED: step 00 seeds the throwaway driver_identity_info row via the mock SQL endpoint \u2014 no manual psql needed. The webhook secret (crc_webhook_secret) must match the running app's Verification_Idfy secret; on the standard config-synced local/CI setup that is the env default 'test-secret'.\n\nPREREQUISITES (environment, already set in Local_NY_Bangalore):\n  1. driverAppWebhookBase points at caddy (8016), which proxies the top-level webhook path to the driver-app.\n  2. mockServerUrl reachable (8080) for the SQL seed/select steps.\n\nNOTE: the CRC *submit* (approval -> verifyCRCAsync) needs an all-docs-verified driver + the per-merchant flag (UPDATE atlas_driver_offer_bpp.transporter_config SET enable_court_record_check = true WHERE merchant_operating_city_id = '<opCityId>'); that path is covered by code review and the gridline mock's ind_court_record handler, not by this collection.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00a - Seed throwaway driver row (self-contained)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('seed driver row 200', function(){ pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"db_name\":\"atlas_dev\",\"db_schema\":\"atlas_driver_offer_bpp\",\"table_name\":\"driver_identity_info\",\"values\":{\"driver_id\":\"{{crc_test_driver}}\",\"merchant_id\":\"{{driver_merchant_id}}\",\"merchant_operating_city_id\":\"{{crc_opcity_id}}\"},\"touch_timestamps\":true,\"on_conflict_do_nothing\":true}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{mockServerUrl}}/mock/sql/insert",
          "host": [
            "{{mockServerUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "mock",
            "sql",
            "insert"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "00 - Reset court_record (clean slate)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('reset 200', function(){ pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"db_name\":\"atlas_dev\",\"db_schema\":\"atlas_driver_offer_bpp\",\"table_name\":\"driver_identity_info\",\"set\":{\"court_record\":null},\"where_clause\":[{\"column_name\":\"driver_id\",\"val\":\"{{crc_test_driver}}\",\"op\":\"=\"}],\"touch_updated_at\":true}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{mockServerUrl}}/mock/sql/update",
          "host": [
            "{{mockServerUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "mock",
            "sql",
            "update"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "01 - Valid CRC webhook (3 cases) -> 200 ACK",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('webhook returns 200', function(){ pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
              "var d = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('ACK status', function(){ pm.expect(JSON.stringify(d)).to.include('ACK'); });"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "{{crc_webhook_secret}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"action\":\"court_record_check\",\"completed_at\":\"2026-06-13T10:00:00Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-13T09:59:00Z\",\"group_id\":\"{{crc_test_driver}}\",\"request_id\":\"crc-newman-1\",\"status\":\"completed\",\"task_id\":\"crc-newman-1-t\",\"type\":\"ind_court_record\",\"result\":{\"source_output\":{\"case_details_link\":\"https://example.com/c\",\"number_of_cases\":3,\"report_download_link\":\"https://example.com/r\",\"risk_summary\":\"3 pending cases\",\"risk_type\":\"high\",\"status\":\"completed\"}}}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{driverAppWebhookBase}}/{{dashboard_merchant_id}}/{{city}}/service/idfy/verification",
          "host": [
            "{{driverAppWebhookBase}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "{{dashboard_merchant_id}}",
            "{{city}}",
            "service",
            "idfy",
            "verification"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - court_record stored + json-queryable (poll)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "if(!pm.collectionVariables.get('_p2')) pm.collectionVariables.set('_p2','0');",
              "var a=parseInt(pm.collectionVariables.get('_p2'))||0; var w=a===0?3000:2000; var t=Date.now(); while(Date.now()-t<w){}"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('select 200', function(){ pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
              "var d = pm.response.json(); var a=parseInt(pm.collectionVariables.get('_p2'))||0;",
              "var cr = (d.rows && d.rows[0]) ? d.rows[0].court_record : null;",
              "if (typeof cr === 'string') { try { cr = JSON.parse(cr); } catch(e){} }",
              "var res = (cr && cr.result) ? cr.result : null;",
              "if (res) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('_p2','0');",
              "  pm.test('court_record result present', function(){ pm.expect(res).to.not.be.null; });",
              "  pm.test('json field risk_type=high', function(){ pm.expect(res.risk_type).to.eql('high'); });",
              "  pm.test('json field number_of_cases=3', function(){ pm.expect(String(res.number_of_cases)).to.eql('3'); });",
              "  pm.test('json field status=completed', function(){ pm.expect(res.status).to.eql('completed'); });",
              "  pm.test('no errorMessage on success', function(){ pm.expect(cr.errorMessage == null).to.be.true; });",
              "} else if (a < 8) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('_p2', String(a+1)); postman.setNextRequest(pm.info.requestName);",
              "} else {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('_p2','0');",
              "  pm.test('court_record result stored within retries', function(){ pm.expect(res).to.not.be.null; });",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"db_name\":\"atlas_dev\",\"db_schema\":\"atlas_driver_offer_bpp\",\"table_name\":\"driver_identity_info\",\"select\":[\"driver_id\",\"court_record\"],\"where_clause\":[{\"column_name\":\"driver_id\",\"val\":\"{{crc_test_driver}}\",\"op\":\"=\"}],\"limit\":1}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{mockServerUrl}}/mock/sql/select",
          "host": [
            "{{mockServerUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "mock",
            "sql",
            "select"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
